dr.inference.operators
Interface OperatorSchedule

All Known Implementing Classes:
CombinedOperatorSchedule, SimpleOperatorSchedule
public interface OperatorSchedule

An interface the defines an operator schedule for use in choosing the next operator during an MCMC run.
